            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1376037194,
            "creation_date": 1376037194,
            "body": "<p>If you want to have a specific format of date on your page, i will advise you to use <code>struts 2  jquery datepicker<\/code>. You can find a demo of this following <a href=\"http://struts.jgeppert.com/struts2-jquery-showcase/index.action\" rel=\"nofollow\">this url<\/a>. Go to <code>widgets<\/code> tab, select <code>datepicker<\/code>.<\/p>\n",
